      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample size and protocol documented by FDA pump study authors.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental dataset is a publicly available reference dataset with documented sample protocol. Formal statistical adequacy assessment of test samples not required at MRL 2."
    },
